  'faq.title': 'Frequently asked questions',
  'faq.q1': 'Is Rebooked TCPA compliant?',
  'faq.a1': 'Yes. Rebooked includes built-in TCPA compliance features: opt-in/opt-out management, quiet hours enforcement (no messages before 8am or after 9pm in the recipient\'s timezone), consent tracking, and automatic suppression of opted-out numbers. We also provide compliant opt-in language templates for your intake forms.',
  'faq.q2': 'How long does it take to set up?',
  'faq.a2': 'Most businesses are fully operational within 15 minutes. Connect your calendar or scheduling system, import your client list, and enable the automations you want. There is no complex configuration -- our 19 pre-built automations work out of the box.',
  'faq.q3': 'What scheduling systems do you integrate with?',
  'faq.a3': 'Rebooked integrates with all major scheduling platforms including Calendly, Acuity, Square Appointments, Mindbody, Jane App, Vagaro, and more. We also offer a REST API and webhook support for custom integrations.',
  'faq.q4': 'How does the revenue share work?',
  'faq.a4': 'You only pay the revenue share on appointments that Rebooked directly recovers. The Rebooked plan has a 15% revenue share and the Flex plan has a 20% revenue share. We track attribution precisely -- if a client rebooks after receiving one of our automated messages, that counts. If they would have booked anyway through your normal channels, it does not. You never pay for revenue you would have earned without us.',
  'faq.q5': 'Can I customize the SMS messages?',
  'faq.a5': 'Absolutely. Every automation template is fully customizable. You can edit the message text, timing, tone, and follow-up sequences. Our AI rewrite feature can also automatically adjust your messages for different tones -- friendly, professional, or urgent -- while maintaining your brand voice.',
  'faq.q6': 'What about HIPAA compliance for healthcare providers?',
  'faq.a6': 'For healthcare clients, Rebooked offers HIPAA-compliant messaging with PHI redaction, encrypted storage, and BAA agreements. Patient appointment details are never included in SMS messages unless explicitly configured with appropriate consent.',
  'faq.q7': 'How does the referral program work?',
  'faq.a7': 'Earn $300 per referral. When someone signs up using your referral code and maintains an active subscription, you receive $50/month for 6 consecutive months. Payouts are processed automatically through Stripe -- no delays, no minimums.',
  'faq.q8': 'What happens if Rebooked doesn\'t generate positive ROI?',
  'faq.a8': 'Our early adopter program comes with an ROI guarantee. If Rebooked doesn\'t recover more revenue than it costs within the first 30 days, we\'ll refund your subscription fee in full. We\'re that confident in our platform.',

